{"tid":2311812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國國防部將中芯國際等4家中資企業列入黑名單","createTime":"2020-12-04T11:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T12:49:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62d55ff69f886c7d7ab379ab277baa73d2e9296c","tid":2311812,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/F4AD28BF-A423-48FC-971A-9821DC165801_cx0_cy6_cw0_w650_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FF4AD28BF-A423-48FC-971A-9821DC165801_cx0_cy6_cw0_w650_r1_s.jpg&h=79245a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政府星期四(12月3日)正式將中國晶片製造商中芯國際(SMIC)與石油巨頭中國海洋石油(CNOOC)等公司列入企業黑名單，此舉可能使得總統當選人拜登上任之前加劇美中之間的緊張關係。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部認定4家中資公司被中國解放軍擁有或控制，另外2家分別是中國建設科技有限公司(China Construction Technology)以及中國國際工程諮詢公司(CIECC)。<br />\n<br />\n目前被列入黑名單的中資企業名單已經達到35家。儘管國防部尚未針對這份黑名單採取任何懲罰性措施，不過特朗普總統近期將發布行政命令，阻止美國投資人自明年下半年起購買黑名單當中企業的有價證券。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美國大使館、中芯國際和中國海油公司暫未回復置評要求。這項消息發布之後，中國海油旗下在香港上市的中國海油股價重挫近14%。<br />\n<br />\n美國認為，中國努力支持企業將新興民用科技用於軍事用途。該名單也是美國針對中國這種做法所採取的廣泛舉措的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n這份&ldquo;中共軍方企業&rdquo;名單是根據1999年的法律編制。這項法律要求國防部編制一份由中國軍方擁有或控制的企業名單，國防部於2020年才編制出該名單。今年稍早，海康衛視、中國電信及中國移動都被加入了這份名單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-dod-on-4-chinese-co-20201204/5687073.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fus-dod-on-4-chinese-co-20201204%2F5687073.html&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=542c9a43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-dod-on-4-chinese-co-20201204/5687073.html</a>"},{"pid":"8f5f604f24369f3beea97ba7a016125f5977d0e6","tid":2311812,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc67b8db8810a2be6cbc1fbd7809217797efc9","tid":2311812,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e3e6adec39534d70292b5a7269e6aa0bb72887","tid":2311812,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"將四年工作壓縮到兩個月"},{"pid":"be75617bbf5507c3550a35ace9511f071a517018","tid":2311812,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續"},{"pid":"b8f833f726578783b37a88116e33195ffe0c7d8a","tid":2311812,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2f9f95e0c0a64c04983d7c29edd1100c555899","tid":2311812,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"香港人歡迎美國制裁行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fca0ee79f5872f3371cfe435d4d42ea80dfec2","tid":2311812,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"華春瑩：你唔可以喧樣對中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係個個都咁衰嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2caaebe350e05295f07c758acfeba35d780f22","tid":2311812,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8faaa1c89f6a68